Class ShadowItemizedOverlay<Item extends com.google.android.maps.OverlayItem>

java.lang.Object
  org.robolectric.shadows.ShadowItemizedOverlay<Item>

@Implements(value=com.google.android.maps.ItemizedOverlay.class)
public class ShadowItemizedOverlay<Item extends com.google.android.maps.OverlayItem>
extends Object

Shadow for ItemizedOverlay that keeps track of what has been called and enables the return value for hitTest(com.google.android.maps.OverlayItem, android.graphics.drawable.Drawable, int, int) to be set up by tests.
